            <div class="postdetail_header">
                <h1><a href="../category-1.htm"  id="backToPostCollect" data-click="onClick" data-block="INNERNAV" data-element="1">讨论区</a><span></span>讨论详情</h1>
                    <div class="posttitle">【学堂暑期大学】夏日学霸大作战（结果已公布）</div>
                    <div class="postref cf">
                        <img class="touxiang_img" src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/users/info/avatar/avatar-370631-20160809113232.png" >

                        <div class="author"><a href="http://bad_redirect" >学堂活动小队长♂</a></div>
                        <div class="last_send_time fr">2016-07-01 11:42:49</div>
                    </div>

            </div>
                <div class="postdetail_contentpart scanimg cf">
                    <div class="postdetail_content" data-innerclick="innerClick" data-block="CONTENT" data-description="PRIMARYINNERNAV">
                        <p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160708/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=132&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="暑期学堂大学广场.png" /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>———</strong><strong>———</strong></strong>————————【 最终结果 】——————————<strong>——<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——<strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>不好意思让大家久等啦！</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span><strong style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>终于到了激动人心发奖环节！</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>恭喜以下获奖的小伙伴！</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></p><p><strong style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></p><p><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160926/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=133&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="巨无霸.jpg" /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160926/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=134&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="大学霸.jpg" /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160926/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=135&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="小学霸.jpg" /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160926/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=201&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="逆袭奖.jpg" /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>【说明与须知】</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">请以上获奖者于近期及时查收站内信，并在<strong>10月14日</strong>前根据要求提供个人信息，以便我们寄送奖品。逾期未回复者视为放弃领奖</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">单项任务的课程认证证书优惠券将于一周之内发送至获奖者账户，请前往<strong>“个人主页”-“优惠券”</strong>一栏查收</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">认证证书优惠券有效期为<strong>4个月</strong></span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">有任何疑问，请私信小队长</span></p></li></ul><div><br /></div><p><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>———</strong><strong>———</strong></strong>————————【 2016.09.26 】——————————<strong>——<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——<strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong></strong></strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>———</strong><strong>———</strong></strong>————————【 规则说明 】——————————<strong>——<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——<strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——</strong></strong></strong></strong><strong><strong>—<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>1、“逆袭奖”专为7月份错过活动的童鞋准备，因此，已申请“巨无霸”“大学霸”“小学霸”的同学</strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>&nbsp; 不再参与“逆袭奖”评选。</strong></span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>2、由于“学堂暑期大学-大学先修课”课程成绩公布时间较晚，请选修了课程又参与了学霸活动的同学</strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>&nbsp; 与9月4日前先行发帖申请认证，成绩公布后工作人员会进行统一审核。过期发帖申请认证视为无效。</strong></span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>3、活动最终获奖名单将于9月下旬在此贴公布。</strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">【小队长的碎碎念】</span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">抱歉啦各位，暑期班的大学先修课结课比较晚，我们的获奖公布时间也相应变晚啦，小队长</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">也无能为力。</span></p><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">不过同学们不要心急，是你的奖总是跑不掉的。</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">这几天小队长很感动，看到很多童鞋发认证贴的时候说，</span></p><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">很感谢学堂在线陪伴他们过了一个</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">充实的暑假，还说了自己在这两个月的收获和心路历程。大家说得这些正是支撑</span></p><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">我们继续这份</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">事业的动力，能为这么多小伙伴带来哪怕一丁点好的改变，一丁点有益的帮助，对我们来说</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">都是极大的</span></p><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">鼓励！</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">感谢大家的支持与肯定！</span></p><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">为了梦想，为了目标，为了成为一个更好的自己。</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">新学期，请大家和我们一起，继续加油吧！</span></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;"><br /></strong></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong><strong><strong>———</strong><strong>———</strong></strong>————————【“八月の逆袭”·学霸追加任务】——————————<strong>——<strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>—</strong></strong><strong><strong>——</strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">好多童鞋找小队长抱怨：哎呀！！！我之前没看到学霸活动的通知啊！！！现在做任务都来不及了啊。。。</span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">哼~~~这下方了吧~~~知道要及时关注我们了吧！！！</span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">行了行了，大家都别再懊恼了，这里就再给大家一次<strong><span style="white-space: normal;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">“</span></span>逆袭<span style="white-space: normal;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">”</span></span></strong>的机会吧！</span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">7月份错过活动的童鞋，这次可别再错过了！！！</span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>在活动截至之前，你只要：</strong></span></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">1. 选修至少2门“学堂暑期大学”课程并拿到1门结课证书，在课程讨论区中至少发言20次，发帖和回贴都算发言</span></strong></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">（在每门课的讨论区中发言都要不少于20次）</span></strong></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;"><br /></span></strong></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">2. 8月份签到不少于25天<span style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;">（手机客户端和网页端皆可签到）</span></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong><br /></strong></span><strong style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;">3. 学习期间在学堂广场至少发布7篇关于所选课程的笔记帖子，帖子标题前请注明【暑期班】</strong><br /></p><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5; white-space: nowrap;"><br /></strong></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;">完成以上3项任务，就能获得我们的<strong>“逆袭奖”</strong>！</span></p><p><strong style="white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5;">逆袭奖10名，奖励价值99元的小米小钢炮蓝牙音箱1台。</strong><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ps</strong>.完成【逆袭任务】的童鞋，请自行在学堂广场申请认证，认证方式见下方<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;">【任务奖励申领<span style="font-family: Calibri;">+</span>学霸认证方式】第3点。</strong></p><p>其余活动规则及活动须知不变。</p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="white-space: nowrap;"><strong>———————————————【以上内容更新于2016.7.29】———————————————————</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><br /></strong></span><br /></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>Summer is coming......</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>烈日灼心，暑期又至。</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>这个夏天，在啤酒烤串儿撸啊撸，旅游唱<span style="font-family:Calibri">K</span><span style="font-family:宋体">斗地主的背后，</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>有这么一群人，他们吹着空调，吃着水果，在学堂在线争夺学霸的宝座<span style="font-family:Calibri">~~~<img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=125&process=0&org=48&course_mode=0"  />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=125&process=0&org=48&course_mode=0-1"  />&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=125&process=0&org=48&course_mode=0-1"  /></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>2016<span style="font-family:宋体">年暑期，学堂在线火热上线“学堂暑期大学”，</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体">大学科，</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">54</span><span style="font-family:宋体">门课程开放学习，认证模式全程开放！</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>这个暑假不无聊，学堂菌让你足不出户，就能网罗名校好课！<img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2550&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  />&nbsp;<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2550&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0-1"  />&nbsp;<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2550&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0-1"  /></strong></strong></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>为了激发小伙伴们的学习意志，小队长特意为大家策划了一场“夏日学霸大作战”！</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>只要你能完成以下一项或几项“学霸任务”，就能领取相应的任务奖励；完成规定的组合任务，更能获得我们准备的“学霸大奖”！</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>夏日炎炎，在家享一份清凉，学一些知识，得几张证书，顺便拿一些大奖，不亦乐乎！！！</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>还在等什么？！赶紧去选课吧！！！</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><a href="javascript:if(confirm('http://www.xuetangx.com/event/courses?credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2783&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0  \n\n���ļ��޷��� Teleport Ultra ����, ��Ϊ ������, ������������, ����Ŀ����ֹͣ��  \n\n�����ڷ������ϴ�����?'))window.location='http://www.xuetangx.com/event/courses?credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2783&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0'"  target="_blank">》》》学堂暑期大学传送门《《《</a></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>【<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2952&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  /></strong>完成任务就能领奖<img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=2952&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0-1"  />】</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>任务一：</strong>在所选修的“学堂暑期大学”课程的讨论区中，至少发言<span style="font-family:Calibri">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">次，发帖和回贴都算发言。（选修了几门课，在每门课的讨论区中发言都要不少于</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">次。）</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>奖励：价值<span style="font-family:Calibri">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元认证证书优惠券</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">张</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>任务二：</strong><span style="font-family:Calibri">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月份签到不少于20天；8月份签到不少于25天</span><span style="font-family:宋体">（手机客户端和网页端皆可签到。）</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>奖励：价值<span style="font-family:Calibri">50</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元认证证书优惠券</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">张</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>任务三：</strong>学习期间在学堂广场至少发布<span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">篇关于所选课程的笔记帖子，帖子标题前请注明【暑期班】。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>奖励：价值<span style="font-family:Calibri">100</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元认证证书优惠券</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">张</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>任务四：</strong>完成暑期班八大类课程各一门，总计<span style="font-family:Calibri">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体">门课程，并通过全部课程考核。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>奖励：价值<span style="font-family:Calibri">150</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元认证证书优惠券</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">张</span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong>暑期课程八大分类如下</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160706/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6"  alt="八大类.jpg" /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>【<strong style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: normal;"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6&course_mode=2"  /></strong>完成组合任务，赢学霸大奖<img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/xuetangx/site/umeditor/emotion/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6&course_mode=2-1"  />】</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>巨无霸<span style="font-family:Calibri">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">名：完成所有任务，奖励价值</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">558</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">kindle</span>电子书阅读器<span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">台</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160701/courses-credential=0&page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6&course_mode=1"  alt="kindle亚马逊.jpg" /></span></strong></span></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">大学霸<span style="font-family:Calibri">30</span><span style="font-family:宋体">名：完成任务一、二、三，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">奖励价值<span style="font-family:Calibri">99</span><span style="font-family:宋体">元小米小钢炮蓝牙音箱1台</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160701/courses-page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="蓝牙音箱_副本.jpg" /></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>小学霸<span style="font-family:Calibri">100</span><span style="font-family:宋体">名：完成任务一和任务二，奖励学堂在线定制笔记本</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">本</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="../../../storage.xuetangx.com/bbs/20160701/courses-credential=1&page_type=0&cid=0&process=0&org=6&course_mode=0"  alt="笔记本111_副本.jpg" /></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体"><br /></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体"><strong>【若各奖项学霸申请人数超过限制人数，学堂在线将会在审核中根据任务完成质量择优选择获奖同学。任务完成质量的审核参考以下标准】：</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">课程考试成绩</strong><br /></p></li><li><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">笔记质量</strong><br /></p></li><li><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">打卡天数</strong><br /></p></li><li><p><strong style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">讨论区发言质量</strong></p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp;</span><br /></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong>暑期班上课时间：</strong>2016年7月1日--2016年9月1日</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong>任务奖励申领及学霸认证时间：</strong>2016年8月25日--2016年9月4日</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>【任务奖励申领<span style="font-family:Calibri">+</span><span style="font-family:宋体">学霸认证方式】</span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体">凡在活动时间之内完成任务的同学们，请于</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月2</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日之后至9月4日之前，在“学堂广场”的“分享”类目下发帖进行任务奖励申领和学霸认证，帖子标题命名规则：</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体"><br /></span></strong></span></p><ol><li><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">完成组合任务，申请学霸认证的同学</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">——“【</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: Calibri;">2016</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">暑期班】学霸认证”，帖子内请注明自己所完成的任务编号。<strong>申请学霸认证的同学无需再次发帖进行任务奖励申领。</strong></span></p></li><li><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">未完成组合任务，仅申领任务奖的同学</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">——“【</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: Calibri;">2016</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">暑期班】任务奖申领”，帖子内请注明自己所完成的任务编号。</span></p></li><li><p><strong style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">完成“逆袭任务”申请认证的同学——“【2016暑期班】逆袭认证”，帖子内注明发言次数、打卡天数和笔记篇数。</strong><br /></p></li></ol><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">*注意：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">请确保发帖账号与学习账号一致，学堂在线工作人员会根据您的账号进行后台审核。</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"><strong>申请“学霸认证”的同学，一个账号仅能申请一类学霸大奖，多个申请视为无效。</strong></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><strong>【活动须知】</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">本次活动各项任务的范围仅限于“学堂暑期大学”课程，其他课程不参与本次活动。</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">认证证书优惠券有效期为<span style="font-family:Calibri">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">个月。</span></span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">学霸奖项不可叠加领取。</span></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">学堂在线将于活动结束后的<span style="font-family:Calibri">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体">个工作日内公布获奖名单并与实物奖获奖用户联系，获奖用户须如实提供个人信息，学堂在线将于确认之后的</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">15</span><span style="font-family:宋体">个工作日内发放奖品，获奖用户如于获奖名单公布后的</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">个工作日内未确认获奖信息，则视为放弃领奖；</span></span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">如遇不可抗力因素，活动因故无法进行时，活动主办方在法律允许的范围内有权决定取消、终止、修改或暂停本活动；</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span><br /></p></li><li><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;">学堂在线保留在法律规定的范围内对上述规则进行解释的权利，若发现作弊等恶意行为，即取消活动参与资格，学堂在线内部员工没有获奖资格</span></p></li></ul>
